Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Good morning, Suzui-san.}Chào cậu, Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah, Jabami-san.}A, Jabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Morning.}Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that won't do at all.}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{We've become friends, haven't we?}Chúng ta là bạn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please call me that.}Như vậy đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{S-Sure!}À-Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,, Y-Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{I owe you a huge debt, don't I?}Tớ còn nợ cậu một khoản nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yesterday...}Hôm qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't pay it back immediately but I'll definitely return it.}Tớ không thể trả ngay nhưng nhất định sẽ trả.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please don't worry about it since it was a gift.}Đừng lo lắng về nó, đó là một món quà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not that I can't pay it back anyway but...}Đúng là khó có thể trả được...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, I can't do that!}Không, không, không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{Flat chested}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.00,Black,,0,0,0,,{Washboard LOL}Bồn rửa LOL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.00,Blue,,0,0,0,,{Ugly} Xấu như chó
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,50)}Mike
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{What in the world is this?}Đây là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did something happen?}Có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you being bulli-}Ai lại làm chuyện--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shut up!}Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,50)}Mike
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{This happened because I lost to you!}Vì tôi thua cô đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and put the tag on.}Nào nào, đeo vô đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you break the rules, your debt will increase.}Nếu phá luật, nợ lại tăng nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,50)}Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hyakkaou Private Academy.}Học viện Hyakkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{There is a caste system in this school.}Được phân biệt giai cấp rõ ràng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your rank isn't determined by your grades or how good you are at sports....}Nó không quyết định bởi điểm số hay khả năng thể thao...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{But your gambling ability.}Mà là khả năng cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{What happened to Saotome isn't your fault.}Chuyện với Saotome không phải lỗi do cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's the rule of this academy.}Đó chỉ là quy luật học viện.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rule?}Luật?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. }Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Since we have a lot of students from influential backgrounds,}Vì trường ta có nhiều học sinh có thế lực,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{the school decided that skills like bargaining, lip reading}nhà trường đã quyết định những kĩ năng như thương lượng, đọc môi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{and the ability to compete are essential for \Nthese students who will eventually become leaders.}sẽ rất cần thiết cho những lãnh đạo tương lai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why people good at gambling will become popular.}Đó là lý do ai giỏi cờ bạc sẽ rất nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Conversely, someone bad at gambling will be persecuted.}Ngược lại, sẽ bị bắt nạt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Specifically speaking, we have a ranking system for students,}Nói kĩ hơn, chúng ta có một hệ thống phân cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{and "Student Council Payments" which\N manages all gambling within the school.}Và "Hội học sinh" sẽ quản lý mọi hoạt động cờ bạc trong trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can elevate your rank with those payments.}Cậu có thể tăng thứ hạng với những khoản thanh toán cho họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{The rankings are announced at irregular intervals,}Bảng xếp hạng thường công bố bất ngờ,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{and if you are the lowest ranked hundred \Nstudents among the three thousand students,}và nếu nằm ở những thứ hạng thấp nhất trên 3000 học sinh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,50)}{Uncooperative Students}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{you will be treated as an uncooperative student A.K.A housepet.}cậu sẽ được coi là học sinh không không có khả \Nnăng đầu tư hay nói cách khác là thú cưng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Male housepets are named Pochi}Nam gọi là Pochi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{while females are named Mike.}nữ gọi là Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{So yours is also...}Vậy cả cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but I got rid of mine by paying 1,000,000 yen.}Ừm, nhưng tớ đã trả được 1 triệu nên thoát rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thanks to you.}Nhờ có cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Congratulations!}Chúc mừng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you very-}Cám ơn cậu rất--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{They weren't treated as harshly in the past.}Ngày xưa ít khi ai bị bắt nạt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{That changed 2 years ago,}Nhưng 2 năm trước,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{when the current student president took office.}từ lúc người đứng đầu hiện tại lên nắm quyền.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Momobami Kirari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{While this is both a middle and high school,}Trường chúng ta bao gồm cả cấp 2 và 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{she transferred here in her first year of high school.}cô ta chuyển đến từ năm nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{And... became the student council president abruptly.}Và...đột nhiên trở thành hội trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{She gambled with the previous president with the position on the line.}Cô ấy đánh bạc với hội trưởng tiền nhiệm để giành vị trí đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wow! Gambling for the position?}Chà! Đánh giành ghế hội trưởng sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Our student council uses the most extreme type of gambling.}Hội học sinh trường ta sử dụng loại hình cờ bạc rất khốc liệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's befitting of those trying to aim for the top.}Nhưng nhắm đến vị trí đứng đầu thì điều đó là đương nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{She carried out some "reform",}Cô ta thực hiện một số "cải cách",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{that's when the "Student Council Payments" and "Pochi/Mike" system came to be.}và lúc đó cái gọi là "Hội đồng thanh toán Hội học sinh"\N và "Pochi/Mike" ra đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's when it started happening.}Từ lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{The discrimination gradually became worse and worse.}Sự phân biệt đối xử càng ngày càng tệ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, Saotome's case is a bit extreme}Mà, trường hợp của Saotome là đặc biệt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{since she had everyone's help, but still suffered a big loss.}dù có nhiều người giúp, cậu ta vẫn thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,100)}{87th Position\N Saotome Mary}Saotome Mary hạng 87
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's also unlucky since the deadline for the payments are drawing near.}Cậu ta cũng xui khi bảng xếp hạng công bố ngay lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry. Did I scare you?}T-Tớ làm cậu sợ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{My goodness.}Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{The more you tell me about this place,}Càng nghe về nơi này,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{the clearer it becomes that it is not a normal academy.}tớ càng thấy nó không phải là học viện bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad that I transferred here!}Thật tốt khi chuyển đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is she not afraid of any of this?}Cậu ta không sợ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Full house!}Sảnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's my victory!}Thắng rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yay!}Tuyệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wow! People gamble during lunchtime too?}Chà, ăn trưa mà mọi người cũng chơi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah, that girl!}A, cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's a first year student and a member of the student council,}Là thành viên hội học sinh dù chỉ mới năm nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{she's kind of popular.}Rất nổi tiếng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did she gamble her way in too?}Vậy cậu ta cũng chơi cờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, I heard that she paid a large sum of money to be let into the student council.}Không, nghe bảo tài trợ cho hội học sinh một món tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Her dad is the president of a prominent toy company in Japan.}Cha cô ta là chủ tịch công ty đồ chơi cực lớn ở Nhật.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not only is she really rich but she's good at gambling too.}Không chỉ giàu mà còn cờ bạc giỏi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{It seems that she's undefeated at card games...}Đặc biệt là bất bại trong chơi bài...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Undefeated?}Bất bại?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's amazing!}Tuyệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{I definitely want to try playing against her...}Tớ muốn chơi thử với em ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, it's best if you don't-}Không, cậu không nên làm thế--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabami-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's nice to meet you!}Rất vui được gặp chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,50)}{Episode 2 A Boring Girl}Tập 2: Ả đàn bà đáng chán
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm a first year from class Flower, Sumeragi Itsuki!}Em là Sumeragi Itsuki, học sinh năm nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's nice to make your accquaintance.}Rất vui làm quen với chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{W-What are you trying to do?}E-Em định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Senpai, you're the talk of the school!}Chị đang rất nổi đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{About how on your first day here you made a fool of Saotome-senpai...}Ngày đầu tiên chuyển trường đã hạ Saotome-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm pretty good at gambling myself, y'see.}Thực ra em cũng rất giỏi cờ bạc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{So I thought it might be fun to compare our skills.}Thế nên chúng ta hãy thử so sánh khả năng xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{I welcome your challenge!}Chị rất vui lòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait, Yumeko!}Khoan, Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{I thought you would.}Phải thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why am I... in this state?}Tại sao mình...lại phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{How did things turn out like this?}Tại sao lại xảy ra chuyện này?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mike! I spilled my coffee.}Mike! Tôi làm đổ coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come clean up the mess.}Lại đây dọn dẹp đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Big news!}Này! Nghe gì chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi Itsuki of the Student \NCouncil is going to have a gambling match!}Sumeragi Itsuki chuẩn bị chơi bạc đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?! Who's her opponent?}Sao? Ai là đối thủ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's the popular Jabami Yumeko!}V.I.P Jabami Yumeko chứ ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you serious?}Đùa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where is it?}Ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{In the cafeteria!}Căn tin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now then, the game we'll be playing is called}Chúng ta sẽ chơi trò
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Double Memory", is that okay?}"Ghi nhớ gấp đôi" nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{As the name suggests, we'll be using two deck of cards.}Như cái tên, chúng ta sẽ dùng hai bộ bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{In normal Memory, you simply match\N up the numbers on the card to get a point.}Trong trò chơi Ghi nhớ bình thường,\N ta chỉ cần nhớ hai lá bài giống số nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{However, in this game, the suit must match as well.}Nhưng trò này thì phải nhớ cả chất của nó nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{In other words, every card only has one match in the 104 card deck.}Nói cách khác, chỉ có hai lá giống nhau trong 104 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nghe thú vị quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{I definitely want to try it!}Chị muốn thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Được!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now, time to talk bets.}Giờ thì nói về tiền cược.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{We'll use twenty 1,000,000 yen chips issued by the student council.}Chúng ta sẽ dùng 20 xèng 1 triệu yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{How does 20,000,000 yen sound?}Tức là 20 triệu nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's a pity but I simply don't have that sort of money on me anymore.}Tiếc quá, chị không còn nhiều tiền như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{I won't be able to prepare 20,000,000 yen to use.}Chị không thể chuẩn bị kịp 20 triệu yên ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? I guess contrary to your appearance,\N you do like to spend money quickly.}Hử? Em nghĩ với ngoại hình đó thì chị cũng sống thoáng lắm chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Or could it be that you had debt to pay off?}Hay chị nợ ai đó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry.}X-Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, no need to worry!}Mà không sao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll lend you 20,000,000 yen!}Em sẽ cho chị mượn 20 triệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Interest free.}Không lấy lãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? What would you gain from doing this?}Em được gì từ vụ này?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{To be honest, 20,000,000 yen \Nreally isn't that big of a deal to me.}Nói thật, 20 triệu là tiền lẻ với em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Getting everyone else interest in my company's cards will be far more profitable in the end.}Cái em muốn là mọi người quan tâm đến bộ bài của công ty em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Plus, it's good for PR.}Chiến lược PR thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{If that's the case, then by all means.}Nếu vậy thì chị chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay, then! We've settled the terms for the gamble!}Được! Chúng ta chơi luôn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{As I mentioned before, we'll be using two brand new decks of cards.}Như em đã giải thích vừa nãy, chúng ta sẽ sử dụng hai bộ bài mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{My company's top product: Raclette.}Sản phẩm của công ty em: Raclette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's the second most popular brand of cards in Japan.}Là nhãn hiệu nổi tiếng thứ hai tại Nhật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{One of it's selling points is how good they feel in your hands!}Rất dễ đánh và dễ cầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please buy some!}Hãy mua nhé mọi người!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is she really promoting it right now?}Em ấy quảng cáo thật à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's start our game of "Double Memory".}Bắt đầu trò chơi của chúng ta nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Go ahead, senpai.}Chị trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll let you have the first move.}Em sẽ nhường lượt đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, thanks.}A, cám ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm... No point in worrying about the first move, right?}Hừm...đầu tiên thì không phải lo lắng gì nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{They both fours but...}Cả hai đều là bốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Under these rules, that's not a match, right?}Nhưng lại không đồng chất nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Exactly.}Chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now it's my turn.}Giờ đến em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to see a Four of Hearts or Diamonds.}Muốn tìm được con bốn cơ hay rô quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Isn't this variation of Memory a bit too hard?}Quả nhiên trò này quá khó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Since there's only one card you can make a match with,}Chỉ có hai lá giống nhau,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{the chances of getting a match by luck is 1/103.}nên xác suất trúng sẽ là 1/103.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{So that means the only real way to win is to \Nremember all of the cards you've flipped over before...}Cách thắng duy nhất là nhớ hết những gì đã lật...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{But there's no way someone could \Nremember the locations of 103 different cards!}Nhưng làm gì có ai nhớ hết nổi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{The King of Diamonds and the Ace of Spades.}Già rô và Xì bích.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's the Two of Hearts...}Đó là hai cơ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{That card is a Club...}Kia là...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is impossible! I'm starting to get a headache!}Không thể! Đầu mình sắp nổ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think a four of Diamonds showed up before.}Hình như lá bốn cơ vừa nãy ra rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was...}Vị trí...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think it was right here.}Ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{I did it!}Biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Since you found a match, you can pick again.}Nếu trúng chị có thể đi tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Go ahead.}Mời.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Seven of Diamonds...}Bảy rô...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{King of Clubs... It's a miss.}Già chuồn...Hụt rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{I remember seeing a King of Clubs before!}Em nhớ vị trí!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Right here!}Chỗ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi isn't losing either.}Sumeragi cũng không chịu thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Amazing... It's a pretty close game.}Tuyệt...đang cân bằng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko has eighteen cards. }Yumeko có 18 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi has twenty two.}Sumeragi có 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Neither is backing down.}Cả hai đang ăn miếng trả miếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Say... This might be just my imagination but...}Này...không biết tao có tưởng tượng không...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Neither of them have made any mistakes in a while, right?}Nãy tới giờ cả hai vẫn chưa lật hụt lần nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, I mean it feels like if they flip up a card they've seen before,}Họ có vẻ đã ghi nhớ hết bài mình đã lật.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{they always remember where it is.}Và chắc chắn điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Five of Hearts.}Năm cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've already seen that once before.}Đâu đây nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{I told you!}Thấy chưa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Does she remember the locations of all the cards she's seen before?}Cả hai đều nhớ hết vị trí lá bài sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{If they're both evenly matched in terms of memory,}Nếu cả hai đều có khả năng ghi nhớ siêu việt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{then it just becomes a match of who is lucky enough to flip over a card whose match they've already seen.}trận chiến chỉ còn là về may mắn xem họ có lật\Ntrúng những con đã mở trước đó hay không.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Only twenty eight left.}Chỉ còn lại 28 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko has thirty six cards.}Yumeko có 36 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi has forty.}Sumeragi có 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's still just as close as ever.}Vẫn đang cân bằng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{But this is where it'll start getting tough.}Nhưng từ giờ sẽ khó khăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{The less cards there are total, the easier it will be to find matches.}Vì ít bài hơn nên đoán cũng dễ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{The game will surely take a turn here!}Chắc chắn đây sẽ là lúc quyết định.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{You sure can gamble, senpai.}Chị chơi được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is the first time I've had a game that was this good.}Đây là lần đầu tiên em chơi trận hay như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh my.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's an honor.}Thật vinh hạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now then, I must focus...}Giờ thì phải tập trung...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah. A match.}A, chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{And then this one...}Và lá này...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is a match as well.}Lại đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Furthermore, this is...}Hơn nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Great!}Tuyệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh? I've seen this before too!}A, em thấy lá này từ trước rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh?}Chà!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've gotten ten cards in a row!}Em lấy được 10 lá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Looks like Lady Luck is smiling upon me!}Có vẻ thần may mắn đứng về phía em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's a difference of fourteen cards...}Còn 14 lá...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{With that big of a gap, it's all over...}Với khoảng cách như thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oops.}Chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's not a match.}Hụt rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're up, senpai.}Đến chị đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{But know that if you miss the next pair,}Nếu lần sau mà tạch là thua đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{I will surely win the game.}Em sẽ thắng trận này.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now do your best!}Cố hết sức đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not a match?}Hụt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{And... I've got a match.}Và...trúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{That means it's my victory since I've gotten the majority of the fifty four pairs, right?}Vậy là em đã chiếm phần hơn của 54 cặp và thắng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{A 20,000,000 yen debt...}20 triệu yên...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you gonna do?!}Cậu tính sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{She said she didn't have that kind of money!}Cậu ấy bảo không mang theo tiền nhiều mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ahaha! I did it! I won again!}Ahaha! Lại thắng nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumeragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can we...}Chúng ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can we play another match?}Chơi thêm trận nữa được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't afford to pay you 20,000,000 yen!}Chị không thể nào trả nổi 20 triệu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have the same ability to remember the locations of the cards as you do!}Chị cũng có khả năng nhớ hết vị trí bài!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{I cannot understand why I lost!}Nhưng không hiểu tại sao lại thua?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please give me the chance to play you once more!}Hãy cho chị một cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Y'see, nails are a hobby of mine.}Chà, thực ra móng tay là thứ em thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look!}Nhìn xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{They're cute, riChúng ght?}Chúng dễ thương chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Of course, this is only a part of my collection.}Dĩ nhiên, đây chỉ là một phần thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{But the truth is... There's a little secret about them.}Sự thật là...có một bí mật nho nhỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{They're all actual human fingernails.}Tất cả đều là móng tay người đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{With the kind of money I have, it would be easy to buy them.}Mua bằng tiền cũng vui nhưng như thế chán lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{But no one will sell actual human nails to me,}Với lại chả ai đi bán móng tay cho em hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{so most of the ones I have were taken as gambling debts.}Thế nên hầu hết chúng là hàng thua bạc cả đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{So I'll put another 20,000,000 yen on the line...}Thế nên, em sẽ lấy 20 triệu ra cược...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{But Senpai!}Nhưng chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want your nails!}Em muốn đống móng tay đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{She can't be serious!}Đùa nhau à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Betting nails...}Lấy móng tay ra cược...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{How about it, Senpai?}Chị thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Y-Yumeko, there is no need to accept such a ridiculous-}Y-Yumeko, đừng chấp nhận--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Very well.}Chị hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{I accept your conditions.}Chị chấp nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are yo-}Cậu sao thế--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{But there's no other way for me to get the money back!}Nhưng chỉ có cách này mới lấy lại tiền thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Unless you want to pay her for me, Suzui-san?}Hay cậu muốn trả thay tớ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's impossible...}Không, tớ chỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's the spirit!}Phải thế chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{We'll use two brand new decks.}Chúng ta sẽ dùng hai bộ mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{You've got to be kidding.}Đùa nhau à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm kinda getting nervous!}Càng ngày càng hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is nuts.}Thật điên rồ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even at this academy,}Dù cả trong học viện này
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{gambling that has physical injury on the line is relatively rare.}thì việc đánh cược nỗi đau thể xác cũng rất hiếm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{But even then, the crowd is really getting excited.}Nhưng mọi người lại thấy phấn khích.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{This isn't some kind of joke!}Đây không phải việc để đùa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shall we begin?}Bắt đầu nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll be betting 20,000,000 yen}Em cược 20 triệu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{while you bet your nails, senpai.}chị cược móng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that okay? }Sao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Feel free to go first.}Mời chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cám ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've got another set for my collection!}Mình sẽ có thêm móng tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm definitely going to win again.}Chắc chắn lần này sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because out of all the face down cards on the table,}Vì một nửa bài trên bàn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{I know exactly where fifty two of them are.}mình đã nắm rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{At first glance, one of the decks we're using might no look any different from my company's normal cards.}Thoạt nhìn những là bài này không khác gì bài thông thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{But the truth of the matter is, it's a special deck from a line that I've personally created.}Nhưng sự thật là mình đã tạo ra vài điểm khác biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's one thing about them that's different from normal cards.}Có một thứ làm nó khác với bài thông thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{If the cards go above a certain temperature, particular marks show up on the back of the cards.}Nếu vượt quá nhiệt độ cho phép, dấu đặc biệt sẽ hiện lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's a circuit in my bag that keeps them warm.}Thế nên mình đã giữ ấm mấy bộ bài trong cặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{So now that they're lined up,}Sau khi hiện lên,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{it's about two or three minutes before they cool back down.}thì chúng sẽ mất đi sau 2,3 phút khi nhiệt độ hạ xuống.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{But until then, the marks remain.}Dấu hiện sẽ vẫn còn trước lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's a very small change, and it goes away quickly.}Chỉ là một dấu nhỏ nên sẽ chẳng ai biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's no way I'll get caught.}Không bao giờ lộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{All I have to do is use that to memorize the cards.}Tất cả còn lại chỉ cần ghi nhớ là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's no way I can lose!}Không bao giờ thua!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{The reason I chose to play "Double Memory" was not only to up the difficulty for my opponent,}Lý do mình chọn trò này không chỉ làm khó đối thủ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{but also to avoid them getting a lucky win.}mà còn tránh cho họ giành chiến thắng nhờ may mắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{No matter if you're playing Poker or Old Maid, }Dù có chơi Poker hay Babanuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{if you know what all the cards are, you'll win.}nếu nhớ hết bài thì ta sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{I had to work hard in order to memorize the marks quickly,}Tuy hơi vất vả để nhớ hết,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{but it paid off in spades!}nhưng phần thưởng cũng xứng đáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll be taking your nails s-}Em sẽ lấy móng tay của chị--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{She got a match!}Mới vào đã trùng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{She got a match on her first turn, that's so lucky.}Quá may mắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{By the way, Sumeragi-san.}Nhân tiện, Sumeragi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{I heard that your family runs a famous toy company, yes?}Chị nghe công ty của em rất nổi tiếng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{With that big of a business, just how much is your family worth?}Với một doanh nghiệp lớn như thế, thì chắc cũng vốn lớn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ten billion yen?}Mười tỷ yên?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Or is it more like a hundred billion yen?}Hay 100 tỷ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{And yet, you're only betting twenty million yen.}Nhưng em chỉ cược mỗi 20 triệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{That somehow doesn't seem worth it, does it?}Tính ra chả thấm vào đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Ý chị là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Allow me to give you one piece of advice.}Để chị cho em một lời khuyên.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Before doing something like betting your parents' business,}Trước khi làm gì đó như mang việc kinh doanh của gia đình ra cược,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{you had best make sure you are duly prepared.}thì phải chuẩn bị tinh thần trước đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? What's she talking about?}Hả? Chị ta nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{My parents' business?}Việc kinh doanh của gia đình?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{It can't be...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{She figured out my trick?}Chị ta nhận ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is she threatening me?}Đang đe dọa mình sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's certainly true that if a toy company were \Nrevealed to be making cards used for cheating,}Đúng là nếu chuyện này bị lộ ra
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{it would cause serious damage to the business!}nó sẽ ảnh hưởng rất lớn đến công ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{How much does she know?}Làm sao chị ta biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did she notice the disappearing patterns on the cards?}Không lẽ nhận ra dấu hiệu sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{No. There's still a chance she's bluffing...}Không. Có khả năng chị ta chỉ lừa mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is bad.}Không ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{With things the way they are, I'll have to flip over all of the cards on my turn, and collect them.}Mình cần phải lấy toàn bộ bài trong một lượt và thu hồi chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Then I'll replace them with a normal deck.}Sau đó tráo bộ bài bình thường vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's all I can do.}Chỉ còn cách đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Once I take my turn...}Một khi đến lượt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{My turn...}Lượt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{My turn...}Lượt của mình....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{My...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumeko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{This makes it fifty four cards.}54 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Which means I win, right?}Chị thắng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{This can't be true...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{How?}Làm sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you were just a bit more careful, I would have lost.}Nếu em nghiêm túc hơn thì chị đã thua rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well... }Vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{The mark on the back of the cards are the same as the last game, right?}Dấu hiệu trên lá bài trùng với bộ trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you'd prepared another deck with a different pattern, } Nếu em chuẩn bị hai bộ khác nhau,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{it'd have been all over for me.}thì có lẽ chị đã thua rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? S-She memorized them all?}Hả? C-Chị ta nhớ hết sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{If that's the case, }Nếu là thế
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{that means she noticed the patterns \Nfrom the very beginning of the first game.}tức là chị ta đã chú ý đến hoa văn ngay từ khi bắt đầu sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{And that she played pretending she didn't know them.}Và giả vờ không biết về nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Her being all upset after losing was just an act.}Lại còn diễn cảnh thua rất đạt nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{But even if that's the case, }Nhưng ngay cả thế
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{the pattern on the cards only show up for about two or three minutes.}dấu hiệu trên lá bài chỉ xuất hiện 2,3 phút thôi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{She would've had to memorize all the patterns first}Chị ta nhớ hết hoa văn trong lần đầu tiên,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{and then connect them to the contents of the flipped cards as they were flipped.}và sau đó liên kết chúng với mặt trước lá bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that even humanly possible?}Chị ta có phải là người không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now, then.}Giờ thì.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{This game is over!}Kết thúc nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's play a different one!}Chơi thêm một trận nữa nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{What shall we play?}Trận sau chơi gì nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Blackjack? What about Baccarat?}Blackjack nhé? Hay Baccarat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{N-No... I-I'm done...}K-Không...T-Tha em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Are you in a position to refuse?}Gì thế? Muốn từ chối chị mày à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah, that's right.}A, đúng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{How about we both put our nails on the line this time?}Lần này chúng ta cược móng tay của cả hai đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{With the terms of "If you lose, you have to have all the nails of your hands and feet ripped off".}Phần thưởng là "Lột sạch móng tay lẫn móng chân" nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,630)}{B-But...}N-Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're the one who came up with that in the first place, so you don't mind, right?}Em là người nghĩ ra trò này mà, nên chắc cũng chịu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've heard that the pain gets worse after the nails are removed.}Chị nghe nói rút móng ra chắc đau lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you put even the slightest burden on your fingers, blood will ooze out.}Máu em sẽ tuôn ra trên những ngón tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{And since we'd be doing it to all of our fingers and toes, it would make everyday life very difficult.}Và nếu mất cả móng chân thì cuộc sống sẽ trở nên khó khăn lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{The idea of having a real match with that kind of risk on the line...}Chỉ nghĩ đến sự nguy hiểm đó thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just imagining it...}Chỉ nghĩ thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{It gets me so excited!}Mà chị đã thấy rất tuyệt rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now then, Sumeragi-san!}Nào, Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is a once in a lifetime opportunity!}Đây là cơ hội ngàn năm có một!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{You confidently cheated in a gamble and still managed to lose.}Dù sự dụng tiểu xảo nhưng vẫn để thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{What will happen if you don't rid yourself of that shame?}Em không muốn rửa nhục hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's do this!}Chơi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{All you need to do is nod your head in agreement.}Tất cả những gì cần làm là gật đầu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now, come on.}Nào nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hurry!}Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's impossible.}Em không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't do it.}Em không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{P-Please... Please forgive me.}T-Tha cho em...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{F-Forgive me.}T-Tha cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Y-Yumeko. She's begging for forgiveness...}Y-Yumeko, em ấy đã cầu xin rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{How boring.}Chán chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{And that's how it ended.}Và đó là mọi chuyện kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{To beat Sumeragi-chan right after transferring in,}Hạ Sumeragi-chan ngay khi vừa chuyển đến
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{the new girl sounds pretty awesome!}học sinh chuyển trường thú vị nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, she was getting cocky over beating small fries.}Thứ rác rưởi đó bị như vậy cũng chẳng lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, Sumeragi did only enter the student council via large payments to us after all.}Chà, Sumeragi chỉ sử dụng tiền để vào hội học sinh thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, and just who was it who gave her a recommendation?}Thế, là ai đã đề cử cô ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shut up.}Im đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, about Jabami Yumeko.}Còn về Jabami Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you going to do about her?}Chúng ta sẽ làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{How interesting.}Thú vị đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why don't we try to meddle with her a bit?}Làm phiền cô ta một chút nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Are you really going to gamble more?}Này! Cậu vẫn muốn chơi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's such a waste if I end like that!}Thì cứ kết thúc như thế phí lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{You said it didn't you, Suzui-san?}Cậu cũng đã nói mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Lots of place on campus turns into gambling dens after school ends.}Mọi nơi trong trường sẽ biến thành sòng bạc sau giờ học.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where are they?}Họ đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's go together, Suzui-san.}Đi với tớ nào, Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Welcome to the Tradtional Culture Club!}Chào mừng đến CLB nghiên cứu Truyền thông văn hóa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{You are in luck, honored guests. \NThere is a public match in progress right now.}Quý khác rất may mắn. Hiện tại đang có một trận đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{How about heading over to watch it?}Xin hãy vào xem thử nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{A public match?}Trận đấu công cộng?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{The result is "Death"!}Kết quả là "Death"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{You have a deficit of 49,600,000 yen.}Số tiền nợ hiện tại là 49 triệu 600000 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{The game is over!}Kết thúc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{F-Forty million?!}B-Bốn mươn chín triệu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{I will be in contact with you later to arrange payment.}Khi nào trả đủ thì xóa nợ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Someone show her outside.}Ai đó dẫn cô ta ra ngoài đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{I no longer have business with her.}Hết giá trị rồi.
